getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.customCond:
EXISTS(SELECT * FROM `IBZDCSYSTEM` t21 
 WHERE 
 t11.`PSSYSTEMID` = t21.`SYSTEMID` AND ( t21.`SRFDCID` =  ${srfsessioncontext('srfdcid','{"defname":"SRFDCID","dename":"SYS_DC_SYSTEM"}')} ) )
getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.name: 查询条件

getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.customCond: EXISTS(SELECT * FROM `ibzemp` t1  WHERE t1.USERID =${srfsessioncontext('srfpersonid','{"defname":"USERID","dename":"IBZUSER"}')}  AND( t1.ADMINUSER ='1' OR t1.SUPERUSER='1'))
getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.name: 查询条件

queryCode:
SELECT
t1.`APPCATEGORY`,
t1.`CREATEDATE`,
t1.`CREATEMAN`,
t1.`ICON`,
t1.`ICONCSS`,
t1.`MOBILEAPP`,
t1.`PERMISSIONTAG`,
t1.`PSSYSAPPFUNCID`,
t1.`PSSYSAPPFUNCNAME`,
t1.`PSSYSTEMAPPID`,
t1.`PSSYSTEMAPPNAME`,
t1.`SHOWORDER`,
t1.`SRFDCID`,
t1.`SYSTEMID`,
t1.`TIP`,
t1.`UPDATEDATE`,
t1.`UPDATEMAN`,
t1.`URL`,
t1.`VIEWPATHPARAMS`
FROM `IBZPSSYSAPPFUNC` t1 
LEFT JOIN `IBZPSSYSTEM` t11 ON t1.`SYSTEMID` = t11.`PSSYSTEMID`
